Most heineous crime.
The  rape of an innocent girl of 8 years in Gopalpur area is a heinous crime.As we know this kind of incident affects the psychology of a tender girl in such way that she never forgets this as long as she lives.This kind of barbarous act ruins a young female both physically and mentally.The sad thing is, the victim is an orphan girl .The district administration must take the incident seriously and punish the capture immediately.
All our members and other like minded media people must see the development of this.Let us try to sensitize this issue without harming the girl .The girl must get all kind of assistance to forget this incident.As responsible citizen ,we should try to create somekind of awareness to prevent this type of gruesome incident.
Moreover,as per the circumstantial evidences and the statement of the raped girl indicates that the culprit may be an armed jawan,the Army AD college authority must take the incident seriously.

